contents.desc: At the US-Saudi investment forum in Riyadh, Saudi Arabia, US President Donald Trump took aim at Iran saying "enemies get you motivated," and declared that the country will "never have a nuclear weapon." Trump is traveling through the Middle East on his first major international trip of his second term. #CNN #news #Trump #SaudiArabia #Iran
